<br>
(A) This is new. Novelty items always bring out the crowds. While this new ability to buy and sell in the Bazaar is *very* cool, and I am sure it will be used heavily from here on, I am also confident that in time we'll see fewer people selling in the Bazaar. This is just the initial novelty rush... <br>
