(B) Use the old models if you're going to spend a considerable amount of time in the Bazaar. <br>
<br>
The way I am going to work it: I am going to plan shopping times. Those times I specifically plan to shop in the Bazaar, I will login with old models. <br>
<br>
Rest of the time, new models. <br>
